1002
00:42:38,931 --> 00:42:39,932
PARK HYE-JEONG

1003
00:42:40,015 --> 00:42:41,433
2024 PARIS OLYMPICS
WEIGHT LIFTING SILVER MEDALIST

1004
00:42:41,517 --> 00:42:43,269
Wait a second.

1005
00:42:43,352 --> 00:42:44,770
