1039
00:44:05,851 --> 00:44:07,227
Okay, hands up.

1040
00:44:07,311 --> 00:44:08,520
- "I pledge."
- "I pledge."

1041
00:44:09,188 --> 00:44:10,189
"One,

1042
00:44:10,731 --> 00:44:13,233
the guest is king and so am I."

1043
00:44:13,317 --> 00:44:14,902
- "So am I!"
- "So am I!"

1044
00:44:14,985 --> 00:44:18,072
"I am my parents' precious child."

1045
00:44:18,155 --> 00:44:19,615
- "Precious child!"
- "Precious child!"

1046
00:44:19,698 --> 00:44:21,033
"And so are you."

1047
00:44:21,116 --> 00:44:22,451
- "So are you!"
- "So are you!"

1048
00:44:22,534 --> 00:44:25,371
"I promise I'm going to have fun here."

1049
00:44:25,454 --> 00:44:26,664
- "Have fun here!"
- "Have fun here!"

1050
00:44:26,747 --> 00:44:31,794
Welcome all, November 2025
participants of <i>Jae-seok's B&B Rules!</i>

1051
00:44:31,877 --> 00:44:33,796
Hands down.

1052
00:44:33,879 --> 00:44:36,256
- Ah! That scared me!
