1053
00:44:36,340 --> 00:44:38,425
STILL JUMPY THE SECOND TIME

1054
00:44:40,260 --> 00:44:41,261
Congratulations!

1055
00:44:41,345 --> 00:44:43,389
WELCOME TO THE B&B

