- Yeah.

1147
00:48:17,352 --> 00:48:19,271
- This is special for us.
- I have great memories from that.

1148
00:48:19,354 --> 00:48:21,690
- I know they're gonna love this.
- Yeah, we're so happy right now.

1149
00:48:21,773 --> 00:48:24,902
