1151
00:48:28,655 --> 00:48:31,325
Please take off your shoes and come on in.

1152
00:48:34,953 --> 00:48:36,455
This is awesome.

1153
00:48:37,289 --> 00:48:38,999
The dorm looks great, doesn't it?

1154
00:48:39,082 --> 00:48:40,459
