1176
00:49:26,922 --> 00:49:29,049
Jo Nam-soon? Nam-soon.

1177
00:49:29,132 --> 00:49:30,759
A couple of towels each.

1178
00:49:30,842 --> 00:49:32,469
SMOOTH SAILING IN THEIR 2ND RUN

1179
00:49:32,552 --> 00:49:34,388
