1184
00:49:48,568 --> 00:49:50,028
You can make guesses like that.

1185
00:49:50,112 --> 00:49:51,989
But don't talk about it directly.

1186
00:49:52,072 --> 00:49:53,448
Anyone hungry?

1187
00:49:53,532 --> 00:49:54,825
Yes!

1188
00:49:54,908 --> 00:49:58,078
