1192
00:50:03,583 --> 00:50:04,584
So don't worry.

1193
00:50:05,168 --> 00:50:06,169
I'll see you in a bit.

1194
00:50:06,253 --> 00:50:07,546
Okay.

1195
00:50:08,213 --> 00:50:10,132
Here we go again. Geez.

1196
00:50:10,215 --> 00:50:11,299
Here we go again.

1197
00:50:12,050 --> 00:50:13,969
Time to focus up.

1198
00:50:14,052 --> 00:50:15,387
I'll chop the kimchi.

1199
00:50:15,470 --> 00:50:17,347
